  <h2>Symphony for Singing Bicycles</h2>
  <p>Performance of Belgian avant garde composer Godfried-Willem Raes' 2nd Symphony for Singing Bicycles A composition scored for 12+ bicycles, dynamos, tubes, speakers, gaffer tape and overalls !!
<br/> <br/>This will take place in Tralee town center on Saturday 20th of April, before the  performance we will be having a workshop to prepare the bikes/instrument. This will start in the square at 3pm and should last about 2 hours. We are still looking for some cyclists to take part in the performance, if you are interested please get in contact or email [ <a href="mailto:axle@kerrybicyclefestival.org?subject=KBF%20Symphony" title="axle@kerrybicyclefestival.org">axle@kerrybicyclefestival.org</a> ] you will need to bring your own bike, all other equipment will be provided. 
 </p>
